1.title: The Land of the Brook
1.plot: Brit and Rach head into the city with their friend, Kennedy, to begin their journey to Brooklyn

2.title: The Burger That's Bare
2.plot: Learn the definition as defined on the always accurate wikipedia and learn that Rach loves more than just 1 percenters.

3.title: ...Over It!
3.plot: Brit and Rach are making friends left and right, as they try to decide what their "ultimate" gentrified neighborhood needs. They hit up Dumbelle and do what they do best at Brooklyn Industries - SHOP.

4.title: Everything's New, Brand New
4.plot: Brit and Rach lost their new clothes and lost their way in Brooklyn. How will they make it to go see their first apartment in a somewhat. - older type of neighborhood?

5.title: To America!
5.plot: Brit and Rach decide they need a little R&R in Brighton Beach after rejecting another apartment suggestion from Kennedy.

6.title: Queens?!?! Shut. Up.
6.plot: Kennedy has lost control of his gal pals, Brit and Rach, as they head to Flushing, Queens with the intentions of seeing Jersey Boys and drinking piña coladas.

7.title: Mama's Empanadas
7.plot: Brit & Rach go to a most unusual "club" and finish the last leg of their long day's journey with a little snack.

imdb.plot outline: Gentrified: a new web series is a satire on and a comedic approach to gentrification. The story is the journey of Brittany and Rachel, two preppy and privileged girls from Connecticut who move out of their parents' houses for the first time to live the NYC life. Most of the action takes place in Brooklyn as the two seek out the best possible neighborhood. Without having the success of finding their perfect spot, deeming Williamsburg too 'hip' and Park Slope too 'suburban', they enlist the help of their friend and real estate broker, Kennedy. This sassy character sends the girls on somewhat of a wild goose chase, as these annoyingly affluent, yet charmingly clueless girls try to gentrify their own neighborhood, as they see fit. With a constantly moving and ever-changing environment, each and every character is played by one of the 4 cast members in the style of SNL. Gentrified truly highlights New York, including the good, the bad, and the funny.
imdb.title: Gentrified
plot: Two suburban girls try to gentrify their own neighborhood in the outer boroughs of New York City in this 7 episodic Web Series.::Anonymous
